<hr>
	2009 Lectures:

<br>	<a href=cos01.pdf> 01 </a>.
	<a href=cos01c.pdf> 01c </a>.
	Review / Overview
<br>	<a href=cos02.pdf> 02 </a>.
	<a href=cos02c.pdf> 02c </a>.
	Distance Ladder.
<br>	<a href=cos03.pdf> 03 </a>.
	<a href=cos03c.pdf> 03c </a>.
	Metrics for curved spaces.
<br>	<a href=cos04.pdf> 04 </a>.
	<a href=cos04c.pdf> 04c </a>.
	Olber's paradox,
	space-time metrics,
	photon paths, conformal time, horizons,
	redshift, time dilation,
	effects on D_A, D_L.

<br>	<a href=cos05.pdf> 05 </a>.
        <a href=cos05c.pdf> 05c </a>.
	time-redshift-distance relation, general relativity, geodesics.

<br>	<a href=cos06.pdf> 06 </a>.
        <a href=cos06c.pdf> 06c </a>.
	Einstein's field equations, Friedmann equation.
	local energy conservation, Newtonian analog, critical density, 
	radiation->matter->vacuum, eqn of state w, Omegas,
	H(x), density->curvature.

<br>	<a href=cos07.pdf> 07 </a>.
        <a href=cos07c.pdf> 07c </a>.
	Dynamics of the Universe:
	H(x)->R(t) for static universe, empty universe, 
	matter-dominated (open, flat, closed),
	radiation-dominated (flat),
	vacuum-dominated (inflation),
	loitering universes.

<br>	<a href=cos08.pdf> 08 </a>.
        <a href=cos08c.pdf> 08c </a>.
	Concordance model, Density parameter evolution, Beyond H0, age constraints

<br>	<a href=cos09.pdf> 09 </a>.
        <a href=cos09c.pdf> 09c </a>.
	Discovery of Dark Energy: q_0, radio jet lengths, hi-z supernovae.	

<br>	<a href=cos10.pdf> 10 </a>.
        <a href=cos10c.pdf> 10c </a>.
	Distance Ladder Checks:
	Sunyaev-Zeldovich effect, Gravitational Lensing


<br>	<a href=cos11.pdf> 11 </a>.
        <a href=cos11c.pdf> 11c </a>.
	Dark Matter, redshift surveys, galaxy counts, 
	luminosity function, mass/light 
	ratios, rotation curves, MACHOs, WIMPs, MOND

<br>	<a href=cos12.pdf> 12 </a>.
        <a href=cos12c.pdf> 12c </a>.
	CMB: COBE, Boomerang, WMAP, Planck.
	recombination, CMB temp maps, power spectra, acoustic 
	peaks, sound horizon, angular scale -> flat geometry,
	Tegmark movies, CMB polarisation, re-ionisation,
	precision cosmology.

<br>	<a href=cos13.pdf> 13 </a>.
        <a href=cos13c.pdf> 13c </a>.
	Large Scale Structure:
	CfA, 2Df redshift surveys, galaxy power spectrum,
	2-point correlation function, Kaiser effect, Fingers of God,
	SDSS, Baryon Accoustic Oscillations.

<br>	<a href=cos14.pdf> 14 </a>.
        <a href=cos14c.pdf> 14c </a>.
	Early Inflation.

<br>	<a href=cos15.pdf> 15 </a>.
        <a href=cos15c.pdf> 15c </a>.
	Early Universe Cooling History.

<br>	<a href=cos16.pdf> 16 </a>.
        <a href=cos16c.pdf> 16c </a>.
	Relic neutrinos.

<br>	<a href=cos17.pdf> 17 </a>.
        <a href=cos17c.pdf> 17c </a>.
	Big-Bang Nucleosynthesis. Primordial He.
